data.description: This historic adobe home and two casitas sits in the coveted Manty Heights subdivision. The price has been reduced as the structures do need work. The value is in the land, a generous 1.2 acer lot in the city with irrigation water, incredible mature landscaping, lush lawns, and beautiful trees. The home and the casitas are livable as they are but require upgrades and structural work as the price reflects. Sold “as is”. Easy to show but must schedule in Showingtime. Home and West casita are vacant, East casita is occupied, do not disturb renter, or enter East casita.
